WEBVTT

00:00:01.438 --> 00:00:05.609 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Imagine a world filled with peace,

00:00:06.610 --> 00:00:08.946 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
free of suffering,

00:00:10.030 --> 00:00:12.741 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
an abundance of food for all,

00:00:13.742 --> 00:00:17.246 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and life in perfect health.

00:00:19.915 --> 00:00:23.544 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But how can this beautiful future
be possible?

00:00:25.045 --> 00:00:28.007 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because of what Jesus did for us.

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:32.761 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He came to earth for a purpose.

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:38.434 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He gave his life for those he loved.

00:00:40.603 --> 00:00:42.605 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The night before he died,

00:00:42.605 --> 00:00:46.442 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jesus asked that we commemorate
his sacrifice.

00:00:47.693 --> 00:00:48.944 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He said:

00:00:48.944 --> 00:00:52.948 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Keep doing this in remembrance of me.”

00:00:55.492 --> 00:00:57.953 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
On the anniversary of his death,

00:00:57.953 --> 00:01:01.290 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
people around the world
will gather to remember him.

00:01:02.333 --> 00:01:05.502 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s Witnesses
invite you and your family

00:01:05.502 --> 00:01:08.797 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to attend the Memorial of Jesus’ death.

00:01:08.797 --> 00:01:11.675 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At that meeting,
you will find out

00:01:11.675 --> 00:01:14.929 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
why his sacrifice was so important

00:01:14.929 --> 00:01:18.140 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and how his promises affect you.

00:01:19.058 --> 00:01:21.560 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To find a location near you,

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:25.481 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
please accept an invitation 
from one of Jehovah’s Witnesses

00:01:25.481 --> 00:01:29.443 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or fill in the congregation
meeting search form

00:01:29.443 --> 00:01:32.780 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on jw.org.

